#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst:2
msgid "管理历史数据的类型——DataType对象"
msgstr "Historical Data Types — the DataType Object"

#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst:4
msgid ""
"DataType 用于以「名称 + 频率 + 资产类型」三元组的方式描述单一历史数据类型，是 数据管线与策略声明历史数据需求时的统一语言。qteasy "
"预置了大量常用 DataType， 也支持通过文档中介绍的接口定义用户自定义数据类型。"
msgstr ""
"``DataType`` describes a single historical data type as a triplet of name + "
"frequency + asset type—the common language for the data pipeline and for "
"strategies to declare data needs. qteasy ships many built-in ``DataType`` "
"instances and supports user-defined types via the documented interfaces."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:1
msgid "qteasy 中用于描述单一历史数据类型（名称、频率与资产类型）的核心对象。"
msgstr ""
"The core object in qteasy for describing a single historical data type "
"(name, frequency, and asset type)."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:3
msgid ""
"每个 DataType 由 ``name``、``freq`` 和 ``asset_type`` 三要素唯一确定，可用于 统一声明策略所需的数据、驱动 "
"``get_history_data_from_source()`` 等内部取数流程， "
"并在需要时扩展出自定义数据类型。关于完整的数据类型表与自定义流程，见文档 「DataType 与历史数据类型管理」章节。"
msgstr ""
"Each ``DataType`` is uniquely defined by ``name``, ``freq``, and "
"``asset_type``. Use it to declare strategy data needs, drive internal fetch "
"flows such as ``get_history_data_from_source()``, and extend custom types "
"when needed. See the “DataType and Historical Data Type Management” chapter "
"for the full type table and customization workflow."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:9
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType:10
msgid "下面示例展示 DataType 类名（稳定输出）。实际创建 DataType 时，需要提供 name/freq/asset_type："
msgstr ""
"The example below shows the ``DataType`` class name (stable output). When "
"creating a ``DataType``, provide ``name``/``freq``/``asset_type``:"

#: of qteasy.DataType.asset_type:1 qteasy.DataType.asset_type_str:1
msgid "资产类型的字符串表示形式，如'E'或'E,IDX'"
msgstr "String form of asset types, e.g. ``'E'`` or ``'E,IDX'``"

#: of qteasy.DataType.asset_types:1
msgid "所用用户定义的资产类型列表"
msgstr "List of user-defined asset types in use"

#: of qteasy.DataType.data_table_names:1
msgid "获取数据表名称，优先使用用户定义的数据表名称，如果没有用户定义的数据表名称，则使用内置数据表名称"
msgstr ""
"Resolve table name(s), preferring user-defined names; fall back to built-in "
"table names if none are defined."

#: of qteasy.DataType.dtype_id:1
msgid "形如：close_E_d"
msgstr "For example: ``close_E_d``"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:1
msgid "数据类型在一天之内开始可用的时间，如收盘价在15:00可用，开盘价在9:30可用，高频数据没有可用时间"
msgstr ""
"Time of day when this data type becomes available (e.g., close at 15:00, "
"open at 9:30; intraday types may have no fixed time)."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:4
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "Properties"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:5
msgid "asset_type: str"
msgstr "asset_type: str"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_available_time:6
msgid "资产类型，如'E'、'IDX'、'FD'等，因为现在支持多资产类型，所以需要指定资产类型以获取对应的可用时间"
msgstr ""
"Asset type such as ``'E'``, ``'IDX'``, ``'FD'``, etc. With multi-asset "
"support, specify asset type to obtain the corresponding availability time."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:1
msgid "Datatype类从DataSource类获取数据的方法，根据数据类型的获取方式，调用相应的方法获取数据并输出"
msgstr ""
"Method for ``DataType`` to fetch data from ``DataSource`` according to the "
"type's retrieval mode."

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:3
msgid "如果symbols为None，则输出为un-symbolised数据，否则输出为symbolised数据"
msgstr ""
"If ``symbols`` is None, returns un-symbolised data; otherwise symbolised "
"data."

#: ../../source/api/data_types.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:5
msgid "数据类型对象"
msgstr "Data type object"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:7
msgid "股票代码列表，一个逗号分隔的字符串，如'000001.SZ,000002.SZ'"
msgstr "Comma-separated share codes, e.g. ``'000001.SZ,000002.SZ'``"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:9
msgid "开始日期, YYYYMMDD格式"
msgstr "Start date, ``YYYYMMDD`` format"

#: of qteasy.datatypes.DataType.get_data_from_source:11
msgid "结束日期, YYYYMMDD格式"
msgstr "End date, ``YYYYMMDD`` format"

#: of qteasy.DataType.id:1
msgid "忽略数据频率的ID形如：close(E)，用于标记不同资产类型的数据"
msgstr ""
"Frequency-agnostic ID like ``close(E)``, marking data for different asset "
"types"

#: of qteasy.DataType.unsymbolized:1
msgid ""
"return True if this data type is unsymbolized data type (i.e. reference data"
" type)"
msgstr ""
"return True if this data type is unsymbolized data type (i.e. reference data"
" type)"
